<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">This sounds like something I ran into some time ago that involved the compiler omitting frame pointers.&nbsp; You may want to try to compile your code with -fno-omit-frame-pointer.&nbsp; I am unsure if you may need to do the same while building MPI
 though.<br>
<br>
--td<br>
